OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry with some low cloud and fog
OL,9,Fpatches.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FLow cloud burning back to
OL,12,Fthe coast in the morning where it may
OL,13,Flinger into the afternoon. Otherwise
OL,14,Fanother dry and sunny day. Very warm
OL,15,Finland, cooler in the east.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FStaying dry with some sunshine, still
OL,19,Fsome low cloud along the east coast.
OL,20,FWarm, locally hot on Thursday in the
OL,21,Fwest. Eastern coastal areas cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
